Source: fluidsynth-headless
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), cmake,
 libasound2-dev, libdbus-1-dev, libglib2.0-dev,
 libjack-jackd2-dev | libjack-dev, libpulse-dev,
 libreadline-dev, libsndfile1-dev, libfluidsynth-dev,
 portaudio19-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: fluidsynth-headless
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libfluidsynth3
Description: FluidSynth CLI binary (headless, no SDL)
 A build of the FluidSynth CLI binary with SDL2/SDL3 disabled,
 suitable for headless pi-Stomp systems. The shared library
 (libfluidsynth3) comes from Debian Trixie apt — this package
 ships only the CLI binary.
